    "The UNIFIEDSKG framework proposed by Xie et al (2022) integrates 21 structured knowledge grounding datasets into a text-to-text format, facilitating systematic SKG research.",
    "This dataset encompasses six task types, including semantic parsing and knowledge base Q&A.",
    "xP3 (Muennighoff et al, 2023b).",
    "The xP3 dataset is a multilingual multitask dataset comprising 82 source datasets spanning 13 task types and 46 languages.",
    "The dataset is fine-tuned on multilingual pretrained models, resulting in variants of models such as BLOOMZ and mT0 (Muennighoff et al, 2023b)."
